ActIndian Act
SubjectAddition to the Rainy River First Nations No. 3, Ontario
PrecisOrder setting apart 0.607 hectare (1.5 acre) of land including mines and minerals for the use and benefit of the Rainy River First Nations as an addition to RAINY RIVER FIRST NATIONS NO. 3, located in the municipal Township of Chapple and is approximately 8 kilometres from the village of Barwick, in Ontario.
